sequenceDiagram
    participant Agent
    participant Memory
    participant BG as Background Thread
    participant Storage

    Agent->>Memory: remember("Client Sarah prefers quarterly reports")
    Memory->>BG: Queue EncodingFlow task
    Memory-->>Agent: Returns immediately (non-blocking)
    Note over Agent: Agent keeps working on other tasks

    BG->>BG: Step 1 - Embed text
    BG->>BG: Step 2 - Dedup check
    BG->>Storage: Step 3 - Search for similar
    Storage-->>BG: Found similar record (0.91 similarity)
    BG->>BG: Step 4 - LLM consolidates records
    BG->>Storage: Step 5 - Delete old + Insert merged
    Storage-->>BG: Saved

    Agent->>Memory: recall("Client contact preferences")
    Memory->>Memory: drain_writes() - wait for pending saves
    Memory->>Storage: Vector search
    Storage-->>Memory: Top results
    Memory-->>Agent: Merged record: "Sarah Chen prefers quarterly written reports"
